name: Aquatic Conservation Club
description: This club's goal is to connect WY to the greater Chicagoland area by preforming service work in Chicago's freshwater systems. We will also educate students on how they could be more green and how their choices impact local ecosystems. This club focuses on the living environment more than abiotic factors! We will provide service learning hours!

announcements.title: Meetings
announcements.description: Club meetings take place Mondays and/or Wednesdays in Room 321/322.
